name: Dam
description:
Celebrating the Photo Day - The World Photography Day - on August 19th, 2021, and every year, everyday in the future, every fraction of a second it takes to shoot a new photo.

With this photo there is an obvious link to OBJKT#142464, please take a look at it. I wish there is magic that happens, in that magical illusion created by your imagination you will see her appearing here. 

Taken in Dam, in Amsterdam by tomi. A long exposure IR shot. 3107 × 2071px.
